{"tid":684572,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(突發)特朗普炮轟「迪士尼」","createTime":"2018-05-30T15:55:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-31T12:48:44.000Z","uid":134071,"like":39,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b855ed267db486ced0fff3c48ceba5778d270266","tid":684572,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T15:55:54.000Z","msg":"Donald Trump心愛劇集《Roseanne》女主角Roseanne Barr因發表種族歧視言論, 迪士尼行政總裁Bob Iger立即下旨腰斬《Roseanne》 (雖然《Roseanne》收視極高).<br />\n<a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/683962/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">http://lihkg.com/thread/683962/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nDonald Trump立即開火炮轟. Donald Trump更指Bob Iger也曾對自己發出侮辱性言論, 但Bob Iger卻從未道歉.<br />\n<a href=\"http://twitter.com/realDonaldTrump/with_replies\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FrealDonaldTrump%2Fwith_replies&d=nXJoC05fDDEosIck8i9fsk%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=b8461d2d\" target=\"_blank\">http://twitter.com/realDonaldTrump/with_replies</a><br />\n<br />\nDonald J. Trump<br />\n&rlm;Verified account @realDonaldTrump<br />\n21m21 minutes ago<br />\n<br />\nBob Iger of ABC called Valerie Jarrett to let her know that &ldquo;ABC does not tolerate comments like those&rdquo; made by Roseanne Barr. Gee, he never called President Donald J. Trump to apologize for the HORRIBLE statements made and said about me on ABC. Maybe I just didn&rsquo;t get the call?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n(但Donald Trump其實吹「迪士尼」唔脹: 杯葛「迪士尼」仲難過杯葛cctvb. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   )"},{"pid":"53e15d50f3ed3e8845602cd22e04a1a79083f788","tid":684572,"uid":132859,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T17:37:29.000Z","msg":"Disney咁玩法,買fox資產嗰陣一定俾trump撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f3f3c8386ce168b29fb2ceddb1dc346ebfaf86e","tid":684572,"uid":126283,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T17:39:33.000Z","msg":"左膠只會選擇性睇/聽某啲事"},{"pid":"90073b9b8fb71fd